<h1 class="alt"><%=h @status %> Error</h1>

<p>You appear to be trying to do something you shouldn't or access a page that doesn't exist.</p>

<p>If this isn't the case, please could you log onto the <%= link_to "BathLARP Bug Tracker", "http://bugs.bathlarp.co.uk", { :target => '_new' } %> 
	and raise a new Support request, explaining what you did to get this error and copying in the text below.</p>
	
<p class="errortext">
	<code>
		<%=h DateTime.now %>
		<% unless @exception.nil? %>
		    <br />
		    <%=h @exception %>
		<% end %>
                <% unless @trace.nil? %>
		        <% @trace.each do |line| %>
			        <br />
			        <%=h line %>
		        <% end %>
                <% end %>
	</code>
</p>
